Revision history for HTML-Laundry

0.01      2009-11-23T12:35:00-05:00

          Support added for non-default rulesets, and Minimal ruleset added as standard option; callback
          syntax altered to support chaining; base_uri getter/setter method; HTML::Tidy::libXML supported
          as backup option to HTML::Tidy

0.0002    2009-10-07T12:03:00-04:00

          Providing a variety of features involving URI parsing: cleaning sample XSS injection techniques
          from ha.ckers.org; support for UTF-8 domains such as tinyarro.ws; tests for URI sanitzation and
          Unicode handling as well as rebasing

0.0001    2009-04-23T08:57:05-04:00

          First version released to GitHub
